'''CenturyTel of Northwest Arkansas, LLC''' is a telephone operating of [[CenturyLink]] providing local telephone services to northwest [[Arkansas]], including [[Siloam Springs, Arkansas|Siloam Springs]]. The company was founded in [[1999]] when CenturyTel purchased access lines in Arkansas from [[GTE]].<ref>http://www.nytimes.com/1999/06/30/business/company-news-gte-is-in-843.3-million-deal-with-centurytel.html?src=pm</ref>
The company has been owned by [[CenturyLink]], which was formerly CenturyTel.
